acl: list: Usage: infinit-acl acl list [OPTIONS]
List ACLs

Options:
  -h, --help                show this help message
      --compatibility-version arg  compatibility version to force
  -s, --script              suppress extraneous human friendly messages and use JSON output
  -a, --as arg              user to run commands as (default: akim)
      --path arg            file whose acl to list
  -R, --recursive           list acl recursively
  -v, --verbose             use verbose output
      --fallback-xattrs     use fallback special file if extended attributes are not supported

